    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，是个闭环。但中间会分叉——遥测数据流要绕一圈经过MQTT broker，再整合回PLC逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出主干：执行器控制器A指向B，然后到边缘节点C，再连到PLC逻辑D。这样前三步没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但B和C的关系要确认一下——B是另一个执行器控制器实例，它把控制指令传给边缘节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，B作为中间控制器实例。现在从D引出遥测数据流E，E应该指向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "E要回到另一个边缘节点F，这个F和前面的C是同类但不同实例，负责汇聚数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
