    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，G负责处理汇聚后的遥测数据，然后它要把数据推送到MQTT broker H。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G",
        "H",
